{"tid":1030840,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友仲有同ex聯絡，點處理","createTime":"2019-02-21T08:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T09:45:24.000Z","uid":153158,"like":120,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"88a83f9fdb527950e40d317c46e3f8497aa1e769","tid":1030840,"uid":153158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:44:47.000Z","msg":"男朋友之前同ex一齊6年，到宜家仲有聯絡<br />\n試過暪住我同ex出去食飯比我發現<br />\n我原諒左佢，因為個ex既問題同佢嘈過幾次交<br />\n但佢話仲聯絡係因為佢真係當ex係朋友<br />\n間唔中問候一兩句實屬正常，因為佢好重情喎<br />\n有時偷睇佢電話發現佢地真係閒聊<br />\n幾日先覆一次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 男朋友係好仔黎<br />\n講大話就會手震面紅所以冇野呃到我<br />\n<br />\n繼續比佢聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男人都係賤分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34217f5791980744710acf2d84b774d3a45a6b74","tid":1030840,"uid":55941,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"可能del撚晒message姐 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e3106e76bdeb1cd798c47509c270fca7840946","tid":1030840,"uid":195364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"屌尻佢跟住分手"},{"pid":"aadd49a23419465825af1de793dedb407827224f","tid":1030840,"uid":123456,"like":18,"dislike":40,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:46:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">男人做野你地啲雞咪咁撚煩</span>"},{"pid":"e45840e34b49ea32d4ce51851fa215150c0c29cf","tid":1030840,"uid":88503,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:52:51.000Z","msg":"大方啲 一齊去食 將佢ex變成你朋友"},{"pid":"02bc27547c86d3c14f7b82e2d82fe337629405e5","tid":1030840,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:06:48.000Z","msg":"接受唔到但唔需要去到分手 可以再同佢傾下"},{"pid":"e1fb4a35c2ee36de7c7fdb8296d94e9123eaaea7","tid":1030840,"uid":153158,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"34217f579198074